2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on interference management in a network, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a new scheme for interference alignment, which can be seen as a control problem in a communication system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with improving the performance of a communication system, which is a key aspect of multimedia systems. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper involves mathematical analysis and optimization of a communication system, which can be seen as a computational engineering problem.
